-- Bear Stearns says worst mortgage write-downs past
-- 
-- Wed Nov 14, 2007 8:49am EST
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2007/11/14/us-bear-stearns-says-worst-mortgage-writ-idUSL1491157120071114

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Bear Stearns Cos Inc's BSC.N chief financial officer said the worst of its mortgage write-downs are behind it. 

 Speaking at a conference on Wednesday, CFO and Chief Operating Officer Sam Molinaro said the current environment is challenging, but the investment bank believes its recorded values for assets reflects those difficulties. (Reporting by  Dan Wilchins , editing by Gerald E. McCormick)